  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Start the day with a delicious hot and cold buffet to build up your energy for a busy day ahead. Dinner is in the hotel's restaurant La Fourchette where you'll get a four course dinner from their a la carte menu. </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>In a resort that screams 5-star luxury, comes a hotel to match, the Grand Hotel Courmayeur Mont Blanc. In a fantastic location, just moments away from the centre of the <a data-udi="umb://document/6001103ad3884b75a70ed71efd274ef8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6001103ad3884b75a70ed71efd274ef8}" title="Courmayeur">Courmayeur,</a> you'll have everything you need right on your doorstep (if you can bring yourself to leave this stunning hotel). The rooms are all decorated in a modern Alpine style and many have a balcony so you can enjoy the surrounding mountain views.</p>
<p>If skiing is not on the agenda or you want a day off, the hotel's spa is the place to be. The huge 500m² Elysium spa has plenty to keep you entertained and blissfully relaxed. After a couple of hours here there's no better way to end the day than to head to the bar and find a table by the window. This is a great place to wind down with a good book and a few drinks.</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 1 hour 45 mins from Turin airport.</p>]]></description>
