  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Twin Rooms </strong>are about 27m² and sleep two people. All rooms have a shower, hair dryer, safe, TV, tea/coffee making facilities &amp; minibar. Connecting rooms are also available.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Twin Rooms </strong>are about 27m² and sleep two people. They have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Twin Rooms </strong>are about 32m² and sleep up to three people (third bed is a single bed). They have a balcony or terrace.</p>
<p><strong>Twin Rooms for sole use</strong> are also available. Please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>are about 42m² and sleep up to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed). They have a bath with showerhead, lounge &amp; balcony.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>All rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
